flowchart LR
    A[Camera Frame] --> B[Frame Sampler]
    B --> C[Edge Inference]
    C --> D[Detection Result]
    D --> E[Condition Evaluator]
    F[SOP Step Definition] --> E
    G[Policy Thresholds] --> E
    E --> H{Step Passed?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Advance Step]
    H -->|No| J[XR Warning]
    H -->|Uncertain| K[Request Retake or Approval]
    I --> L[Evidence Snapshot]
    J --> L
    K --> L
    L --> M[Object Storage]
    E --> N[Audit Event]
    N --> O[PostgreSQL / Event Queue]
    O --> P[Admin Dashboard]
